OL,3,CPaedophile former police officer loses
OL,4,Cappeal against life sentence
OL,6,FThe paedophile former police officer
OL,7,Fadmitted more than 150 offences and
OL,8,Fwas sentenced to 13 life sentences
OL,9,Fwith a minimum term of 12 years for
OL,10,Fthe most serious charges in October
OL,11,Flast year.
OL,13,FLawyers for the 24-year-old challenged
OL,14,Fthe sentence at the Court of Appeal,
OL,15,Farguing at a hearing on Thursday that
OL,16,Fthe judge should not have passed a
OL,17,Flife sentence.
OL,19,FBut three judges dismissed his appeal.
