OL,6,FCardiff Crown Court heard last year
OL,7,Fthat he threatened to bomb the house
OL,8,Fof one victim and shoot her parents if
OL,9,Fshe stopped sending him images, with
OL,10,Fmany victims self-harming, feeling
OL,11,Fsuicidal and developing anxiety and
OL,12,Fdepression as a result of Edwards's
OL,13,Foffending.
OL,15,FEdwards, who joined South Wales Police
OL,16,Fin January 2021 and resigned during
OL,17,Fcriminal proceedings, met all but one
OL,18,Fof his victims while he was an officer
OL,19,Fand had contact with his victims on 30
OL,20,Foccasions while on duty.
